  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The aim of this element of the HPP programme in CAR implemented by Concern Worldwide is to reinforce availability and access to safe water and sanitation for the people of Kouango sub-prefecture. Key activities include increasing access to clean water; improving hygiene knowledge; increasing public access to clean water at the central hospital, and 4 other public institutions; influencing the adoption of improved hygiene and nutrition practices.</narrative>
